wiki.content: The long overdue official album from VON debuts after 20+ years! The wait is finally over! VON creator "Venien" enters the Von Records studio "THE PIT" to record 19 classic songs from the incubation period, the "Demo Years" of VON. Von Records is proud to announce the official release of Satanic Blood Full Length album from VON! Satanic Blood (Full Length) comes available only in a 12"x12" 20pg booklet w/mounted album CD inside the back cover. CD includes 19 tracks with songs like: Satanic Blood, Watain, Jesus Stain, Devil Pig, Veadtuck, and many more. The included booklet contains 17 illustrated images by VON creator Venien himself. Also included are full lyric sheets and liner notes. Satanic Blood (2012 Full Length) Tracklisting: Jesus Stain Devil Pig Venien Release Veadtuck Vennt Evisc Goat Christ Dissection InHuman Chalice of Blood Blood Von Christfire Backskin Watain Blood Angel Lamb Satanic Blood Satan *Bonus CD Booklet Track Litanies of Von *Bonus CD Booklet Track Vocals: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura Background Vocals: JGiblete "Lord Giblete" Cuervo Bass: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura Guitars: JGiblete "Lord Giblete" Cuervo Drums: Charlie Fell *Studio Sessions ONLY Lyrics written by: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura & Shawn "Goat" Calizo Music written by: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura & Shawn "Goat" Calizo Produced by: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura Mixed by: Andrew Ragin / Wall To Wall Studios (Chicago, IL) Mastered by: John Gray / The Jungle Studios (Scottsdale, AZ) Engineered by: Jason "VENIEN!!!" Ventura, JGiblete "Lord Giblete" Cuervo, Andrew Ragin, & Frank Caruso Recorded at: The PIT (Litchfield Park, AZ) *except drum tracking Recorded at: Wall To Wall Studios (Chicago, IL) *drum tracking only Illustrations and Design: VENIEN!!! Release Date: October 31st 2012 Format: CD Booklet/Digital Label: Von Records Distribution: Von Records Read more on Last.fm.
